{"tid":1269814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［香港有愛］需要支持同鼓勵既你，歡迎入黎取暖","createTime":"2019-06-30T16:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T22:13:44.000Z","uid":138060,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7fd79667b085c4d4fa1f0607808b9f50381f37e7","tid":1269814,"uid":138060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:27:44.000Z","msg":"見到好多放負post，巴絲無曬希望，話要離開我地<br />\n一打開連登見到d標題就精神緊張<br />\n<br />\n希望用愛去洗洗版，歡迎灰心既大家入黎取暖<br />\n留底各位既唔開心情緒，我地係度互相加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">大家唸下，原來我地一路以來已經行左好遠路啦！睇下大家多個月以黎幾厲害，做左幾多樣嘢，喚醒左幾多人，揚威國際</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">所有努力都唔會白費㗎，要相信希望，黑中有光，因為大家都陪伴大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 訓醒繼續一齊上路，我地創造緊自己既歷史！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我地唔好放棄，同大家一齊撐到落尾，好唔好呀</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd7aa4781011149cad86b385a97acba509102ac","tid":1269814,"uid":138060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076ecca6ab2d54dbd051a7ae020e6de2b2f2f750","tid":1269814,"uid":138060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:28:58.000Z","msg":"加油呀"},{"pid":"0a2ed0ff9a93e921677b7bb4bd4af2f03e13eab2","tid":1269814,"uid":138060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"無論你係邊度，都希望你有個好夢"},{"pid":"40050e593c2dffecb4515bcf77b5cfd11c7ea22b","tid":1269814,"uid":138060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"我地會一路陪住你㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54629788127db919e735adb7eb1a6b89b088fad5","tid":126